* 0.3
 - Multiple phone numbers can be generated at once.
 - There are now command line arguments for specifiying how many numbers to generate, and the area code.
 - Exception handling has been implemented to handle bad user input.
* 0.2
The program can now generate phone numbers in all the areas given drama numbers by Ofcom.
* Publication at 0.1
